  "title": "我做了一套揚州話表情包",
  "summary": "by 新世界的大门",
  "content": "<p>受 <a href=\"https://estela.moe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Estela</a>（@saeziae）改作加零貼圖而成的 Everything Wu 的啟發，我也做了一套 Everything Huai。</p>\n<p>閣下可以 <a href=\"https://t.me/addstickers/juaisticker\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">點選此處</a> 添加 Telegram sticker pack。</p>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/乖乖.png\" alt=\"乖乖\" width=\"256\" height=\"221.5\"><div><h2>乖乖</h2><p>表達驚訝、驚歎或不滿。</p></div>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/八折貨.png\" alt=\"八折貨\" width=\"256\" height=\"221.5\"><div><h2>八折貨</h2><p>詈語，程度比較重。</p><p>八折讀音似北方官話的「吧唧」。</p></div>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/不醜.png\" alt=\"不醜\" width=\"256\" height=\"237\"><div><h2>不醜beh4ceu42</h2><p>/pəʔ4 tsʰɤɯ̽42/ 頗好，不是醜的單純否定。</p></div>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/自敢嗌脫.png\" alt=\"自敢嗌脫\" width=\"256\" height=\"221.5\"><div><h2>自敢嗌脫zigaen yih--teh</h2><p></p>自敢\n/tsɿ53 kæ̃42/ 自己<p></p><p></p>嗌\n（貶義的）喫<p></p><p></p>脫\n相當於北方官話中的掉。也在吳語中使用。<p></p><p><strong>例句</strong>：</p><blockquote>\n<p>這瓜要是不甜，你自敢把它嗌脫。</p>\n</blockquote></div>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/假好喃2.webp\" alt=\"假好喃\" width=\"256\" height=\"221.5\"><div><h2>假好喃</h2><p>怎麼辦呢？實際讀音近似 じゃっほーに。可以聽\n<a href=\"https://www.douyin.com/video/6933086930389290255\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">這個視頻</a> 的最後（00&lt;23&gt;）。<sup><a href=\"https://blog.xinshijiededa.men/everything-huai/#user-content-fn-jhn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1</a></sup></p></div>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/8424.png\" alt=\"8424\" width=\"256\" height=\"221.5\"><div><h2>8424</h2><p>長三角流行的一個西瓜品種，揚州以「沙頭 8424」最為知名。</p></div>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/在哪塊啊.png\" alt=\"在哪塊啊\" width=\"256\" height=\"221\"><div><h2>在哪塊啊ze55 la42kua</h2><p>在哪裏？</p><p>哪裏叫做「哪塊」，其中「塊(kue)」的聲母弱化，並且可與「啊」合音爲 kua。</p></div>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/斜下子.png\" alt=\"斜下子\" width=\"256\" height=\"237\"><div><h2>斜下子qia21 haze</h2><p>Take a nap. 注意此處「斜」的讀音，與其他詞中的都不同。</p></div>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/喫過㖸.png\" alt=\"喫過㖸\" width=\"256\" height=\"235\"><div><h2>喫過㖸</h2><p>打招呼的方式之一，約等於北佬所說的「吃了嗎？您內！」。末尾的「㖸」是揚州話的語氣詞，普通話裏這個字也讀作「niā」。你應該在歌曲《楊柳青》裏聽過：</p></div>\n\n<img alt=\"\">\n<img alt=\"給 RSS 閱讀器的——楊柳青\">\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/桀紂-genjyu.png\" alt=\"桀紂\" width=\"256\" height=\"256\"><div><h2>桀紂</h2><p>不順心之事，做事出紕漏。<sup><a href=\"https://blog.xinshijiededa.men/everything-huai/#user-content-fn-jz\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2</a></sup></p></div>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/我是歡𢜶的人-2.png\" alt=\"我是歡𢜶的人\" width=\"256\" height=\"228.5\"><div><h2>我是歡𢜶的人</h2><p>歡𢜶(huaen21 so0)，快樂、歡快的意思，也可以是快的意思。</p></div>\n<p>𢜶（<span>⿰</span><span>忄</span><span>叜</span>）是一個<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hans/%E4%B8%AD%E6%97%A5%E9%9F%93%E7%B5%B1%E4%B8%80%E8%A1%A8%E6%84%8F%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E6%93%B4%E5%B1%95%E5%8D%80B\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">擴 B</a>的字，連<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-cn/%E9%81%8D%E9%BB%91%E9%AB%94\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">遍黑體</a>（Plangothic）都沒有這個字。比如在<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV13jDNYNE29/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">【上海话直译】APT.翻译成上海话应该是？</a>中：</p>\n<div></div>\n<figure><img src=\"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/lEJSvVsRuyDmK9vCbsCGPeNr_lcfudtln0Y3i2hX6wfX6jRoedOu7PM3WVQjU8kpzsEq-A58CBAbb_7f72FvNW_6omWUB_2MUrJd9R6FFGvwf65_6ODnX5t3on2zqjVa.png\" alt=\"侬豪（忄叜）来寻我白相　我就勒海\"><figcaption>侬豪（忄叜）来寻我白相　我就勒海</figcaption></figure>\n<p>於是只好拆開以下字，用部件拼成：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>快的忄</li>\n<li>淀的宀</li>\n<li>燚的火（右上）</li>\n<li>設的又</li>\n</ul>\n<p>累死我了。</p>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/電綫杆.png\" alt=\"隑到電綫杆\" width=\"256\" height=\"256\"><div><h2>隑到電綫杆</h2><p>加零的標誌性動作。隑是靠的意思。</p></div>\n<hr>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/OverflowCat/everything-huai@master/萊斯.png\" alt=\"萊斯\" width=\"256\" height=\"221.5\"><div><h2>萊斯</h2><p>來自 <span>nice</span> 的音譯。注意不是「來事」，兩者意思不同。</p></div>\n\n<h2>附：拼音表<a href=\"https://blog.xinshijiededa.men/everything-huai/#附拼音表\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span>#</span></a></h2>\n<p>僅包含韻母部分。<sup><a href=\"https://blog.xinshijiededa.men/everything-huai/#user-content-fn-wp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">3</a></sup></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th><strong>開口呼</strong></th><th>IPA</th><th>例字</th><th><strong>齊齒呼</strong></th><th>IPA</th><th>例字</th><th><strong>合口呼</strong></th><th>IPA</th><th>例字</th><th><strong>撮口呼</strong></th><th>IPA</th><th>例字</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>i</td><td>ɿ</td><td>滋治是</td><td>i</td><td>i</td><td>地祭米憶</td><td>u</td><td>u</td><td>布樹夫無</td><td>ü</td><td>y</td><td>女居許玉</td></tr><tr><td>a</td><td>a</td><td>巴家<sub>白</sub>打兒</td><td>ia</td><td>ia</td><td>家<sub>文</sub>斜蝦牙</td><td>ua</td><td>ua</td><td>瓜誇瓦</td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td>ê</td><td>ɛ</td><td>太開街<sub>白</sub></t